Lamina command skills (`lamina-init`, `lamina-design`, `lamina-verify`) have **disable-model-invocation**. The harness (or user) must send each step as a **slash-command user message**.

**This session already started with `/lamina-init` above.** Complete init, then continue in order. **Do not write application source until after `/lamina-init` and `/lamina-design` have run.**

