2. **Implement (next user turn, not a Lamina command)** — full product from **`run.yaml` + `implement.md`** + the task brief, in application source outside `.lamina/`.
3. **`/lamina-verify`** — post-build verification under `.lamina/runs/<run_id>/` only.
4. **Fix (next user turn, not a Lamina command)** — apply product fixes from `fix.md` in application source.

Use `.lamina/runs/<run_id>/` layout (`run.yaml`, `implement.md`, `report.md`, `fix.md`).

